dct_title_s: Farming, dairy and timber lands in the Mille Lacs region : located on the new Soo Line traversing this famous district of Minnesota
dct_description_sm: Shows township, range and section lines.; Shows portions of Mille Lacs, Kanabec, Morrison, Crow Wing, Aitkin and Benton Counties.; In pencil: "Found with 1915 material."; At bottom of sheet: "Keep your eyes on the Mille Lacs Region and you will see the best opportunity for the landseeker, the ideal location for a home. For particulars, prices and terms apply to G.R. ZICKRICK, Wahkon, Minnesota."
